<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessage?topicID=245.topic">pub94.ezboard.com/ffirion...=245.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Now as for a mod joining in on these so called attacks is complete trash. Shintou had everything coming to him that he got and more. This wasn't some select case where I wanted to join the &quot;bandwagon&quot; and start bitching at him. Frankly, I was sick of the crap he would post and I unlike some people, I say what I feel and will stand behind it. Sure, I could have just deleted his posts, or locked them, like the other mods do, but I am pretty laid back and let people say what they wanna say. Thats imo part of being a mod, this whole you have to say what I tell you to say, otherwise I will delete it crap doesn't fly well with the big T. <br>
<br>
Now just because someone is this so-great roleplayer doesn't exempt him from any of the other RULES that are stated on this board. There has been people that have done MUCH LESS than Shintou has and have been banned for it ie: Fuvi. Frankly I think that is bullshit and I'll say it right now, and its all because alot of people see him as a very good roleplayer they let him go on his merry way of bitching and cussing at everyone over level 40 without ANY cause whatsoever.<br>
<br>
If you honestly think that all the whining and bitching that he did up to the point did not warrant some kind of reply I suggest you really go back and look over all the crap that was posted by him. He got about 1/20th of what he dished out by me. Thats giving him the benefit of the doubt. Look it sucks that someone had to delete their character and cry themselves to sleep because he got cussed at, but you know what, it goes with the territory. You start swearing at people, chances are someone is gonna say something back. Now just because alot of people respect and like someone does not give them free reign over what they can do. Board rules were set-up when the board was made and apply to everyone, including mods. I don't go around pushing my opinion on anyone on this server, or board and really don't care what you do with them(within reason) but when you go around changing rules and other shit just to suit one person is crap. It doesn't really matter now anyways, whoever the other mods are don't agree with me on that and its pretty self evident, hell even my posts are deleted by someone. That is admin abuse. Me, telling someone to quote &quot;F$ck off&quot; after he intentionally tried to cause shit on these boards is not. You don't believe me? The last post in the mod board before I said anything was about possibly banning Shintou. Now, IMO that would have been abit harsh on anyone that has even come to this board. <br>
